 {"id":"bd-244","title":"Implement SQLiteStorage.CreateIssues with atomic ID range reservation","description":"Core implementation of CreateIssues in internal/storage/sqlite/sqlite.go

Key optimizations:
- Single connection + transaction
- Atomic ID range reservation (generate N IDs in one counter update)
- Prepared statement for bulk inserts
- All-or-nothing atomicity

Expected 5-10x speedup for N>10 issues.","design":"Implementation phases per ULTRATHINK_BD222.md:

1. **Validation**: Pre-validate all issues (calls Issue.Validate() which enforces closed_at invariant from bd-224)
2. **Connection & Transaction**: BEGIN IMMEDIATE (same as CreateIssue)
3. **Batch ID Generation**: Reserve range [nextID, nextID+N) in single counter update
4. **Bulk Insert**: Prepared statement loop (defer multi-VALUE INSERT optimization)
5. **Bulk Events**: Record creation events for all issues
6. **Bulk Dirty**: Mark all issues dirty for export
7. **Commit**: All-or-nothing transaction commit

See ULTRATHINK_BD222.md lines 344-541 for full implementation details.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2025-10-15T14:21:53.433641-07:00","updated_at":"2025-10-15T18:31:28.771539-07:00","closed_at":"2025-10-15T18:31:28.771539-07:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-244","depends_on_id":"bd-222","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2025-10-15T14:21:53.435109-07:00","created_by":"stevey"},{"issue_id":"bd-244","depends_on_id":"bd-240","type":"blocks","created_at":"2025-10-15T14:21:53.43563-07:00","created_by":"stevey"},{"issue_id":"bd-244","depends_on_id":"bd-241","type":"blocks","created_at":"2025-10-15T14:22:17.181984-07:00","created_by":"stevey"},{"issue_id":"bd-244","depends_on_id":"bd-242","type":"blocks","created_at":"2025-10-15T14:22:17.195635-07:00","created_by":"stevey"}]}
